Package org.activebpel.rt.axis.bpel.deploy

Root package for the Active Endpoints Axis specific deployment code.

          Description

Class Summary
AeAxisBase Base class for handling Axis web service deployments.
AeAxisPolicyMapper Abstract class to help map Axis specific details of deploying policy for a web service.
AeAxisWebServicesDeployerBase WebServicesDeployer impl that deploys web services to Axis.
AeAxisXPathPolicyMapper Creates Policy Deployment for a XPath mapping assertions
AeBprDeployment Bpr deployment extends the wsdd deployment of axis for monitoring and setting classloaders used for contexts.
AeCredentialPolicyMapper Creates Policy Deployment for a XPath mapping assertions
AeResourceProvider This class extends the axis file provider so we can create our own deployment context, which can then be classloader aware.
AeWsddBuilder Builder class for creating a wsdd deployment document.
